name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Stock Up: DeFi, NFT and Web3 Extension

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Harness the power of Instant web3 research on 1000s of crypto and nft projects right while you browse the web.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Stock Up research helper tool provides you detailed research docs for every NFT Collection and DeFi and Crypto Project all across Web3 Ecosystem, also we provide you with embedded helpful data right within Opensea & LooksRare marketplaces. No need to switch to another tab, no need to search for data across the web. 

Get live data about new collection launches and activities within the space.

StockUp.Tools is helping investors to make the right decisions by providing timely and quality data about NFTs. And now you can get to the right data even faster.

One extension to make your research needs fulfilled.
